abstract: There is a long path ahead, and we walk it not just for us, but for all those who will come after us; so they don't have to suffer as we did.

headline_main: Transgender Lives: Your Stories: Sophie Lynne

abstract:
One day, my fiancé tendered, “Have you realized that you’re a guy yet?”  

“Oh,” said I, “That makes sense.”
